Product Description

True Human Emperor anti theft backpack ( LEGEND )

Perfectly designed Bag

The bag is aesthetically designed and hand crafted by experts to ensure consistent superior quality and high value for customers . To meet your day to day need, The Laptop Backpack is a lightweight, multi-utility bag .

Ease of Access

Multi purpose pockets Super sorted stuff It has a vibrant and stylish design, along with the added benefit of spacious interiors.

Anti - Theft Pocket

Hidden storage pocket for important documents like passports, tickets, cash while on the go.

The best in class Anti-Theft

This back pack is a stylish and functional accessory for men and women. Can add admiration to an appealing and daring personality with a remarkable aesthetics and functionality.

Integrated Fast charging port

  • Unique pre-fitted USB port helps you to easily connect your phone or any other device with your power bank. Charging system for smart devices , with free USB (power bank not included )

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
